data.enText: a list of the topics, books, etc. that students should study in a particular subject at school or college

tr: an integrated course of academic studies
example: he was admitted to a new program at the university

value.def: You can refer to the subjects that are studied in a particular course as the syllabus .

example.tran: 英国中等教育证书考试的历史大纲

value.def: A syllabus is an outline or summary of the subjects to be covered in a course.
